1.3.1.name: wordpress/milyen-nap-van-most
1.3.1.description: The plugin will display a question in your comment form. This question must be answered correctly otherwise the comment will be rejected. The question and the answer is in Hungarian, so it is intended for blogs that receive comments only from people speaking Hungarian.
